# Runtime-installed binaries land here (uv.sh installs uv/uvx; claude is the
# Claude Code launcher). They are large/machine-specific and must not be
# committed. The `fan` CLI is a tracked repo script, so keep it.
.local/bin/*
!.local/bin/fan
